], [[Nikki Cross]] \n|[[WWE Women's Tag Team Championship]]\n|2\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[World championships in WWE]]\n* [[Women's championships in WWE]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{WWE}}\n\n[[Category:WWE tag team championships| ]]\n[[Category:Tag team wrestling championships]]\n", "name_user": "JDC808", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eBy wrestler", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tag_team_championships_in_WWE"}
{"title_page": "1967\u201368 Midland Football League", "text_new": "The '''1967\u201368 Midland Football League''' season was the 68th in the history of the [[Midland Football League (1889)|Midland Football League]], a [[association football|football]] competition in [[England]].\n\n==League==\n{{Infobox football league season\n|competition= Midland Football League\n|season=1967\u201368\n|winners= [[Ilkeston Town F.C. (1945)|Ilkeston Town]]\n|promoted= [[Gainsborough Trinity F.C.|Gainsborough Trinity]]<br>[[Goole Town F.C.|Goole Town]]<br>[[Scarborough F.C.|Scarborough]]<br>[[Worksop Town F.C.|Worksop Town]]\n|relegated=\n|matches= 420\n|total goals= 1409\n|prevseason= [[1966\u201367 Midland Football League|1966\u201367]]\n|nextseason= [[1968\u201369 Midland Football League|1968\u201369]]\n}}\n\nThe league featured 21 clubs which competed in the previous season, no new clubs joined the division this season.\n\n===League table===\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|use_goal_ratio=y\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=ILK|name_ILK=[[Ilkeston Town F.C. (1945)|Ilkeston Town]]\n|team2=HEA|name_HEA=[[Heanor Town F.C.|Heanor Town]]\n|team3=ARN|name_ARN=[[Arnold F.C.|Arnold]]\n|team4=GAI|name_GAI=[[Gainsborough Trinity F.C.|Gainsborough Trinity]]\n|team5=GOO|name_GOO=[[Goole Town F.C.|Goole Town]]\n|team6=GRA|name_GRA=[[Grantham F.C.|Grantham]]\n|team7=SCA|name_SCA=[[Scarborough F.C.|Scarborough]]\n|team8=LEU|name_LEU=[[Long Eaton United F.C.|Long Eaton United]]\n|team9=WOR|name_WOR=[[Worksop Town F.C.|Worksop Town]]\n|team10=ALF|name_ALF=[[Alfreton Town F.C.|Alfreton Town]]\n|team11=MAT|name_MAT=[[Matlock Town F.C.|Matlock Town]]\n|team12=SUT|name_SUT=[[Ashfield United F.C.|Sutton Town]]\n|team13=LOC|name_LOC=[[Leamington F.C.|Lockheed Leamington]]\n|team14=RET|name_RET=[[Retford Town F.C.|Retford Town]]\n|team15=BEL|name_BEL=[[Belper Town F.C.|Belper Town]]\n|team16=GTR|name_GTR=[[Grimsby Town F.C.|Grimsby Town]] reserves\n|team17=STA|name_STA=[[Stamford F.C.